# Laravel Pulse

- **Package**: [laravel/pulse](https://laravel.com/docs/12.x/pulse). Real-time monitoring dashboard at `/pulse` (admin only).
- **Gate**: `viewPulse` in `AppServiceProvider::boot()` — allows users who `can('access admin panel')` (same as Horizon).
- **Config**: `config/pulse.php` — storage (database/Redis), ingest, middleware, recording.
- **Storage**: Default driver is database; Pulse migrations create the required tables.
- **Response cache**: `pulse/*` is excluded in `PublicContentCacheProfile`.
- **Pan**: Dashboard quick link uses `dashboard-quick-pulse` (whitelisted in `configurePan()`).

See **docs/developer/backend/pulse.md** for full documentation.
